stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CI_Build: git push to main

    CI_Build --> Dev_Deploy: CI passes
    Dev_Deploy --> Dev_Tests: Deploy to dev namespace
    Dev_Tests --> Staging_Gate: Smoke tests pass

    Staging_Gate --> Staging_Deploy: Automatic promotion
    Staging_Deploy --> Staging_Tests: Deploy to staging
    Staging_Tests --> Prod_Gate: Integration tests pass

    Prod_Gate --> Canary: Manual approval / change record
    Canary --> Prod_Analyse: 10% traffic canary
    Prod_Analyse --> Full_Rollout: Error budget OK\n(Argo Rollouts / Flagger)
    Prod_Analyse --> Rollback: Error budget breached

    Full_Rollout --> [*]
    Rollback --> Staging_Gate: Investigate and retry

    CI_Build --> [*]: CI fails — notify developer
